{"tid":962665,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"港航遭母公司海航入稟 追討8.5億","createTime":"2018-12-31T04:56:41.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-31T12:51:54.000Z","uid":66271,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"e6c1c9b0c8f8d7fb58dfbbce0be599ec0d7762d7","tid":962665,"uid":66271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-31T04:56:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181231/large/1546227321_4ae3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181231%2Flarge%2F1546227321_4ae3.jpg&h=c7ad8b3c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n香港航空近日傳出財困消息，除了有五名高層「跳機」辭職外，《蘋果》早前發現港航有一筆高達約43億港元的債券需要償還。港航的母公司、傳與王岐山家族關係密切的海航集團，日前入稟高等法院，要求港航相關公司就一張海航於2010年12月30日發出的本票還款，金額高達8.5億港元。惟入稟狀未有進一步透露詳情。<br />\n<br />\n原告為海航集團（香港）投資有限公司，被告為香港航空咨詢服務有限公司。<br />\n根據公司註冊處資料，早前離任的港航董事鍾國頌，是被告公司的唯一股東及董事。鍾國頌是被外界稱為港航姊妹公司、海航同樣有份投資的香港快運之執行董事長，有報道指鍾與海航關係密切。<br />\n【案件編號：HCA3003/18】<br />\n記者蘇曉欣"},{"pid":"ba4529f45332bdb16d0721277521305258f8d190","tid":962665,"uid":17429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-31T04:56:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f277b3ad20ecb1834c020cf8148a923d1c477fb3","tid":962665,"uid":191926,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-31T04:58:53.000Z","msg":"港航到底可以捱到幾時<br />\n<br />\n叫連尼住 搞競猜活動<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93579563ee3ecc54164a3b75af37143748a04b19","tid":962665,"uid":28195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-31T05:06:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GM6nke8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGM6nke8.png&h=669b4d5c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c3e50daf7530454b0b25d95e848375f90c920f78","tid":962665,"uid":28195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f277b3ad20ecb1834c020cf8148a923d1c4